STEPS TO START A JENKINS FUNCTIONAL CONTAINER

docker build -t centos:jenkins .

docker run -it --name jenkins_container_4 -p 8080:8080 b5893784640f

after logging into the container 

go to path where jenkins.war is available

cd /usr/share/java/

run the below command

java -jar jenkins.war

first time copy the password and save it for the first time login

ctrl+pq to come out of the container without stoping the jenkins service


